Class GrosseEintrag

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pizza.CMModel.DBConnect
      • com.pizza.CMModel.GrosseEintrag

  • public class GrosseEintrag
extends DBConnect

    Models the Grosse Entry of the Grosse Table

    The GrosseEintrag class is used to model the Grosse Table of the database. In addition to getters and setter of the corresponding fields, there is a method used to store a new entry to the table.
